http://dev.mysql.com/doc/connector-python/en/connector-python-installation-src-unix.html

1) Download
On UNIX-like systems such as Linux distributions, Solaris, Apple Mac OS X, and FreeBSD,
 you can download Connector/Python as a tar archive
from http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/python/.

2) Install
shell> gunzip mysql-connector-python-1.0.6b1.tar.gz
shell> tar xf mysql-connector-python-1.0.6b1.tar
shell> cd mysql-connector-python-1.0.6b1
shell> sudo python setup.py install

3) 